    <div
      class="max-w-sm px-2 py-12 mx-auto leading-normal text-center xs:text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl sm:max-w-md md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-white text-opacity-80">Subscribe to <span
          class="font-normal text-white text-opacity-100 whitespace-nowrap">Maybe Now</span> â€” a monthly email with our
